    public class DefaultPortableViewCompiler
extends Object
implements PortableViewCompiler

    Default PortableViewCompiler

    The compilation process is defined by a ProcessStep list which will be call sequentially

    To share process status data between steps every ProcessStep receives a ProcessData instance create before excution's starting
